org.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM custom_emojis LEFT OUTER JOIN custom_emojis AS local_counterparts_custom_emojis ON local_counterparts_custom_emojis.domain IS NULL AND local_counterparts_custom_emojis.shortcode = custom_emojis.shortcode LIMIT "$1" OFFSET "$2"
